<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Tracking Code Help</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --night: #0f1b2d;
            --steel: #24415d;
            --ember: #c85c2b;
            --sand: #f4efe7;
            --paper: #fcfaf5;
            --line: #d6c8b7;
            --text: #1a2430;
            --muted: #5c6a78;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            color: var(--text);
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(200, 92, 43, 0.15), transparent 28%),
                linear-gradient(180deg, #e6ebef 0%, var(--sand) 100%);
        }

        .shell {
            width: min(1240px, calc(100vw - 32px));
            margin: 24px auto 40px;
        }

        .hero {
            display: block;
            padding: 28px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 27, 45, 0.98), rgba(36, 65, 93, 0.92));
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(15, 27, 45, 0.2);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
        }

        .hero p {
            margin: 0;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84);
            line-height: 1.55;
        }

        .hero-nav {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .hero-nav a,
        .hero-nav button {
            border: 0;
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #12314b;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .panel {
            margin-top: 22px;
            background: var(--paper);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 22px;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 44px rgba(36, 65, 93, 0.08);
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .panel h2 {
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
            color: var(--night);
        }

        .breakdown-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .code-box {
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 14px;
        }

        .code-box .code {
            font-family: Consolas, Monaco, monospace;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--steel);
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .example {
            margin-top: 12px;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #e6d8c9;
            background: #fff;
            font-family: Consolas, Monaco, monospace;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--steel);
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 0.93rem;
        }

        th,
        td {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 10px 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e6d8c9;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        th {
            color: var(--steel);
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .mono {
            font-family: Consolas, Monaco, monospace;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        @media (max-width: 980px) {
            .shell { width: min(100vw - 20px, 1240px); }
            .breakdown-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            table { font-size: 0.86rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="shell">
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-nav">
                <a href="/app">Builder</a>
                <a href="/history">History</a>
                <a href="/account">My Account</a>
                {% if is_admin %}
                <a href="/settings">Settings</a>
                {% endif %}
                <a href="/help/tracking-codes" aria-current="page">Tracking Code Help</a>
                <button id="hero-logout" type="button">Logout</button>
            </div>
            <h1>Tracking Code Logic</h1>
            <p>Each tracking code is built as 3 + 3 + 6 characters. This page explains what each block means and maps all current type/subtype combinations.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="panel">
            <h2>Code Breakdown</h2>
            <div class="breakdown-grid">
                <article class="code-box">
                    <div class="code">First 3</div>
                    <div><strong>Type code</strong> identifies the high-level document family.</div>
                    <div>Example: <span class="mono">NET</span> = Network-related documents.</div>
                </article>
                <article class="code-box">
                    <div class="code">Second 3</div>
                    <div><strong>Subtype code</strong> identifies the exact template inside that family.</div>
                    <div>Example: <span class="mono">003</span> = Network Update template.</div>
                </article>
                <article class="code-box">
                    <div class="code">Last 6</div>
                    <div><strong>Date code</strong> uses document date in <span class="mono">YYMMDD</span> format.</div>
                    <div>Example: <span class="mono">260324</span> = 2026-03-24.</div>
                </article>
            </div>
            <div class="example">Example full code: <span class="mono">NET-003-260324</span></div>
        </section>

        <section class="panel">
            <h2>Tracking Code Grid</h2>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Document Name</th>
                        <th>Key</th>
                        <th>Category</th>
                        <th>First 3 (Type)</th>
                        <th>Second 3 (Subtype)</th>
                        <th>Pattern</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for item in document_types %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ item.name }}</td>
                        <td class="mono">{{ item.key }}</td>
                        <td>{{ item.category }}</td>
                        <td class="mono">{{ item.type_code }}</td>
                        <td class="mono">{{ item.subtype_code }}</td>
                        <td class="mono">{{ item.type_code }}-{{ item.subtype_code }}-YYMMDD</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </section>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.getElementById("hero-logout")?.addEventListener("click", async () => {
            await fetch("/auth/logout", { method: "POST" });
            window.location.href = "/";
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
